Class Student

java.lang.Object
Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
User
public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements User
Represents the Student object, unique to the matricID and username variable, each student will have a specific matricid and username. each student are allowed to store multiple course object as long as the object course code is not the same. student can be parttime / fulltime
Since:
2020
